title: What would Sabine Wren think about Earth? - Quora

response.answer_text: Honestly? She wouldn’t really have many different opinions to anyone else from Star Wars stumbling on our planet. Our tech is weirdly both more primitive and slightly advanced compared to theirs.I’m pretty sure our population density is quite high compared to a number of planets.We aren’t unified like so many other planets seem to be are constantly fighting among ourselves.Honestly, she’d just think Earth is a really weird planet. If there is one thing that she would be interested in, it’s our art. An artist like her would likely be interested in the work of an alien culture like our own.
